### Tell name - STM
POST http://localhost:8080/api/short
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "My name is Andrei"
}

### Ask name - STM
POST http://localhost:8080/api/short
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is my name?"
}

### Tell name - LTM
